<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chess Game - Instructions</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center py-12 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">📜 How to Play</h1>

    <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg max-w-lg text-lg space-y-4">
        <p>♙ White always moves first.</p>
        <p>🖱 Drag and drop pieces to make your move.</p>
        <p>🏆 If your opponent disconnects, you win automatically.</p>
        <p>👀 Spectators can watch but cannot move pieces.</p>
        <p>🔥 Enjoy your game!</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/" 
       class="mt-10 px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-lg text-xl font-semibold shadow-lg transition">
        ⬅ Back to Home
    </a>
</body>
</html>
